Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.91,0:23:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Final·Is·Beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.50,0:23:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,————————OP—————————
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:22.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Let's go! 来吧 Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:25.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不论到何处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:30.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}都要紧紧怀抱「相信」的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:49.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}舍弃「以后再说」的念头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:53.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}没有我们见不到的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:01:00.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}唯有鼓起勇气尝试挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:05.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}才能够将想法化为闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.98,0:01:07.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}轻轻吹着口哨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:08.56,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}打打节拍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:10.29,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}对彼此摆鬼脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:11.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Smiling
